The Iron Front rallies for the militant defense of the republic against the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">fascists</span> paramilitaries, strengthening the Reichsbanner.

[? if strife < 5: The <span style="color: #000000;">**Center Party**</span> decries the militarization of the Reichsbanner, and its members are leaving the republican organization. ?][? if strife >= 5: Seeing the strife that has filled Germany's streets, the <span style="color: #000000;">**Center Party**</span> and <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> seem to be convinced that it is necessary for the Reichsbanner to be militarized, and mute their criticisms. ?]


