The <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazis</span> and other far-right political movements are increasingly turning their hatred against the <span style="color: #005EB8;">Jewish</span> community of Germany. The Iron Front rallies in defense of individual <span style="color: #005EB8;">Jews</span> and the broader community against violence.
